data.description: RECENTLY REDUCED IN PRICE AND OFFERING $5,000 IN SELLER CREDITS TO BE USED FOR RATE BUY DOWN OR CLOSING COST! This phenomenal 4 bed 2 bath fully fenced in home on .24 of an acre with a STUNNING pond view is located in the sought after Winding River Community! As soon as you open the front door you are able to see straight through to the pond located outback via the open-concept layout. Walk through large main hallway to the tremendous kitchen with its grand breakfast bar, in addition to a full walk in corner pantry. This kitchen is sure to meet any potential families entertaining needs. At the front of the home you will find three perfectly sized bedrooms along with a full walk in laundry room. The spacious master bedroom is located in the back of the home just off the living room. The oversized master bathroom with soaking tube is a much welcomed retreat after a long busy day. Did we mention all the amenities winding river has to offer?  A 24 hour fitness center, community pool with a kiddie pool, walking paths, soccer fields and so much more! Don’t let this home slip through your fingers! Call today for a showing.
